<div class="content">
  <h4 class="tag-intro" >A tag is a keyword or label that categorizes your question with other, similar questions. Using the right tags makes it easier for others to find and answer your question.</h4>
<h4 class="tag-intro">Clicking a tag will bring you to a page with all the posts under that tag.</h4>
  <% @tags.each do |tag| %>
    <ul class="tag-link"> <%= link_to tag.description, tag_path(tag), :class => "tag-link" %></ul>
  <% end %>
</div>
